data.description: Buyers Financing Failed, HOME APPRAISED!  Seller open to Rent / Lease to own with 5% down minimum.  Beautifully upgraded home, POOL RESURFACE COMPLETED, NEW PICTURES ADDED! featuring 6 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and located CLOSE TO DISNEY in Indian Ridge.  Property has been fully updated since 2018, new roof and AC in last 2 years PLUS new solar system which features almost 12,000 KWH of power generation!  Solar panels will transfer with sale and are OWNED!  Live here, Short term, or Long Term rent in the community.  As you enter into the home the garage is on the right and the office / 6th bedroom is on the left.  Travel further in and you will find the open living area as well as the eat-in-kitchen complete with upgraded cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops!  Out back your very own NEWLY RESURFACED Screened In, Heated, Private Pool!  So much space for you and your guests, updates everywhere, new roof, new AC, new pool surface, plus a fantastic location make this property perfect, come check it out today!
